# Sample Repository

Welcome to your sample repository! This repo demonstrates the basic structure and content for a typical GitHub project.

## Features

- Example code and documentation
- Simple project structure
- Instructions for setup and usage

## Getting Started

To get started, clone this repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/sample-repo.git
cd sample-repo
```

## Usage

Edit files as needed and commit your changes:

```bash
echo "Hello, World!" > hello.txt
git add hello.txt
git commit -m "Add hello.txt"
git push
```

